schools.name: D J Red Simon Middle School

data.description: Stately 2 Story, Stucco home with an oversized backyard for family entertainment, sports or the animal lover in you!  The downstairs includes an office/craft room, a formal dining area, a large living area that opens to the kitchen.  The kitchen has an island w/ a breakfast bar, a desk space for the operations of the home and still plenty of counter space for cooking and helpers!  Upstairs you will appreciate the primary bedroom suite being separated by the game room.  Upstairs laundry room keeps the living upstairs !
